.TH TRANCE 1 "June 2026" "trance" "Trance Screensaver CLI"
.SH NAME
trance \- control interface for the trance screensaver daemon
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B trance
[\fICOMMAND\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B trance
is the CLI for controlling the trance-daemon screensaver monitoring service. It allows query of status, forcing transitions, toggling options, and previewing effects.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B status
Print the active configuration and daemon status.
.TP
.B enable
Enable the idle-saver triggers.
.TP
.B disable
Disable the idle-saver triggers.
.TP
.B start
Trigger the idle saver now.
.TP
.B stop
Deactivate any active fullscreen screensaver presentation.
.TP
.BI preview " <saver>"
Launch a plugin presentation preview in fullscreen.
.TP
.BI set-saver " <saver>"
Set the active screensaver plugin name.
.TP
.BI set-timeout " <minutes>"
Set the idle timeout in minutes.
.TP
.BI set-gpu " <on|off>"
Enable or disable wgpu-based hardware upscaling.
.TP
.BI set-fps " <on|off>"
Enable or disable the FPS counter overlay.
.TP
.BI set-scale " <percentage>"
Set render scaling filter grid size (e.g. 50, 75, 100).
.TP
.B doctor
Run diagnostics on the system idle inhibitor and DBus services.
.SH AUTHOR
Screensavers Developer <dev@local76.org>
